00:01:36.054 --> 00:01:37.055 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Kimura?

00:01:37.138 --> 00:01:38.098 position:50% align:center
[KIMURA]
Here.

00:01:38.181 --> 00:01:39.307 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Gotou?

00:01:39.391 --> 00:01:40.183 position:50% align:center
[GOTOU]
Here.

00:01:40.266 --> 00:01:41.309 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Takahashi?

00:01:41.393 --> 00:01:42.185 position:50% align:center
[TAKAHASHI]
Here.

00:01:42.268 --> 00:01:43.561 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Hasegawa?

00:01:43.645 --> 00:01:46.606 position:50% align:center
[WINDOW MONSTER 09A groaning]

00:01:46.690 --> 00:01:47.691 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Fujita?

00:01:47.774 --> 00:01:48.608 position:50% align:center
[FUJITA]
Here.

00:01:48.692 --> 00:01:49.693 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Horiguchi?

00:01:49.776 --> 00:01:50.610 position:50% align:center
[HORIGUCHI]
Here.

00:01:50.694 --> 00:01:51.945 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Mochida?

00:01:52.028 --> 00:01:53.113 position:50% align:center
