Here!

00:01:53.196 --> 00:01:56.324 position:50% align:center
[WINDOW MONSTER 09A
continues groaning]

00:01:56.408 --> 00:01:57.450 position:50% align:center
[YAMAZAKI]
Here.

00:01:57.534 --> 00:01:58.576 position:50% align:center
[ZEN]
Yurikawa?

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.120 position:50% align:center
[HANA]
Here!

00:03:39.135 --> 00:03:41.930 position:50% align:center
[HANA giggles] I'll take
three of those, please!

00:03:42.013 --> 00:03:43.181 position:50% align:center
