You've been eating all day.

00:03:51.106 --> 00:03:53.108 position:50% align:center
Time of the month?

00:03:53.191 --> 00:03:55.527 position:50% align:center
[HANA] If you snack in secret,
it doesn't count.

00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:56.861 position:50% align:center
