00:04:01.157 --> 00:04:03.618 position:50% align:center
[MIKO sighs]

00:04:03.702 --> 00:04:05.036 position:50% align:center
Like Summer.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:07.122 position:50% align:center
And Winter and Spring.

00:04:07.205 --> 00:04:09.457 position:50% align:center
[HANA]
Ugh! Rude!

00:04:11.126 --> 00:04:14.337 position:50% align:center
[HANA] Anyway, tell me where
we know our teacher from!

00:04:14.421 --> 00:04:16.923 position:50% align:center
Your memory is
way better than mine!

00:04:17.007 --> 00:04:18.174 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:04:18.258 --> 00:04:19.592 position:50% align:center
[HANA] It's been driving
me nuts all morning--

00:04:19.676 --> 00:04:21.386 position:50% align:center
I haven't been able
to think straight.

00:04:21.469 --> 00:04:22.554 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Hm.

00:04:27.392 --> 00:04:29.269 position:50% align:center
Um, I've never seen him before.

00:04:29.352 --> 00:04:30.311 position:50% align:center
[HANA]
Really?

00:04:30.395 --> 00:04:31.312 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:04:31.396 --> 00:04:33.023 position:50% align:center
[HANA groans]
Whatever.

00:04:33.106 --> 00:04:36.609 position:50% align:center
Clearly, I need more food
to power my memory banks.

00:04:36.693 --> 00:04:39.070 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] If Hana had seen
those things surrounding him,

00:04:39.154 --> 00:04:41.239 position:50% align:center
she wouldn't've
forgotten so easily.

00:04:41.322 --> 00:04:44.117 position:50% align:center
But thankfully, he doesn't
seem to remember us either.

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:45.744 position:50% align:center
[HANA gasps]

00:04:45.827 --> 00:04:48.872 position:50% align:center
I got lunch bread, but I forgot
my after-lunch bread!

00:04:48.955 --> 00:04:51.458 position:50% align:center
I think you might need to
get your head checked, Hana.

00:04:51.541 --> 00:04:54.544 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry! Go on without me.
I'll be right back!

00:04:54.627 --> 00:04:56.129 position:50% align:center
Hey!

00:05:01.301 --> 00:05:02.969 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:05:06.973 --> 00:05:08.516 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
If Hana remembers who he is,

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:11.519 position:50% align:center
it'll only mean
more trouble for us.

00:05:11.603 --> 00:05:14.439 position:50% align:center
I have to find a way
to keep her distracted.

00:05:16.274 --> 00:05:19.611 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] Oh, this Halloween
event looks pretty cute.

00:05:19.694 --> 00:05:21.613 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:05:24.532 --> 00:05:26.242 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:05:30.121 --> 00:05:31.664 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:05:55.271 --> 00:05:58.525 position:50% align:center
[MIKO panting]

00:06:07.951 --> 00:06:11.663 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] That was messed up!
I can't escape this guy!

00:06:11.746 --> 00:06:14.499 position:50% align:center
How am I supposed to
ignore this stuff every day?

00:06:14.582 --> 00:06:16.626 position:50% align:center
And what was with
those handprints?

00:06:16.710 --> 00:06:20.296 position:50% align:center
--[footsteps]
--[gasps]

00:06:23.341 --> 00:06:25.760 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Did it follow me?

00:06:28.888 --> 00:06:30.724 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
No, no, no!

00:06:33.518 --> 00:06:37.272 position:50% align:center
[footsteps continue]

00:06:41.901 --> 00:06:43.278 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:06:43.361 --> 00:06:45.155 position:50% align:center
C'mon, lemme just
check real quick.

00:06:45.238 --> 00:06:48.074 position:50% align:center
Nobody cares! Your contacts
look fine, I swear.

00:06:48.158 --> 00:06:49.784 position:50% align:center
[MORINO]
They're totally wonky!

00:06:49.868 --> 00:06:51.161 position:50% align:center
[YAMAZAKI]
Like, how?

00:06:51.244 --> 00:06:53.747 position:50% align:center
[MORINO grunts] See?
The color's all muddy looking!

00:06:53.830 --> 00:06:54.914 position:50% align:center
This is lame.

00:06:54.998 --> 00:06:56.499 position:50% align:center
What does that even mean?

00:06:56.583 --> 00:06:57.751 position:50% align:center
C'mon, let's go get lunch!

00:06:57.834 --> 00:06:59.294 position:50% align:center
Fine, whatever then.

00:06:59.377 --> 00:07:02.047 position:50% align:center
For real though, your
eyelashes are killing it today.

00:07:02.130 --> 00:07:03.381 position:50% align:center
--[MORINO] You can tell?
--[YAMAZAKI] Yeah.

00:07:03.465 --> 00:07:04.924 position:50% align:center
[MORINO] Looks like
I got them done, right?

00:07:05.008 --> 00:07:06.926 position:50% align:center
[YAMAZAKI]
Yep!

00:07:07.010 --> 00:07:08.636 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:07:11.222 --> 00:07:15.393 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Okay, I gotta just calm down.

00:07:17.395 --> 00:07:19.689 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps, whimpers]

00:07:19.773 --> 00:07:22.484 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Shoot, I reacted!

00:07:22.567 --> 00:07:26.321 position:50% align:center
[TOILET MONSTER 09A groans]

00:07:31.284 --> 00:07:33.244 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Oh, crap, oh, crap!

00:07:34.829 --> 00:07:37.082 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Stop!

00:07:37.165 --> 00:07:38.416 position:50% align:center
It's huge!

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.085 position:50% align:center
[TOILET MONSTER 09A groans]

00:07:40.168 --> 00:07:42.295 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:07:42.379 --> 00:07:44.673 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
I let my guard down!

00:07:44.756 --> 00:07:47.384 position:50% align:center
[TOILET MONSTER 09A grunting]

00:07:47.467 --> 00:07:50.929 position:50% align:center
[exhales]

00:07:57.310 --> 00:08:00.897 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Go away, go away, go away!

00:08:02.232 --> 00:08:04.234 position:50% align:center
Uh!

00:08:04.317 --> 00:08:06.945 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Wait, I can play this off!

00:08:09.656 --> 00:08:12.200 position:50% align:center
Ugh... This one's empty.

00:08:12.283 --> 00:08:14.869 position:50% align:center
I'll have to go
to the next stall.

00:08:20.208 --> 00:08:22.168 position:50% align:center
[TOILET MONSTER 09A groans]

00:08:22.252 --> 00:08:23.503 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
It's watching.

00:08:23.586 --> 00:08:25.171 position:50% align:center
Come on, please.

00:08:25.255 --> 00:08:26.756 position:50% align:center
[YULIA gasps]

00:08:34.597 --> 00:08:36.766 position:50% align:center
[YULIA grunts]

00:08:42.313 --> 00:08:46.693 position:50% align:center
'Kay, well, this isn't
anything like I imagined.

00:08:46.776 --> 00:08:48.236 position:50% align:center
Tastes like a mistake.

00:08:48.319 --> 00:08:50.238 position:50% align:center
You figured that out just now?

00:08:50.321 --> 00:08:51.865 position:50% align:center
Hey, Yulia, want some?

00:08:51.948 --> 00:08:53.199 position:50% align:center
I'm good.

00:08:53.283 --> 00:08:54.784 position:50% align:center
[HANA]
Are you, though?

00:08:54.868 --> 00:08:57.495 position:50% align:center
With love, not eating enough's
a sure way to stunt your growth.

00:08:57.579 --> 00:08:59.664 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] Got outta that
by the skin of my teeth.

00:08:59.748 --> 00:09:01.624 position:50% align:center
Pull it together!

00:09:01.708 --> 00:09:05.378 position:50% align:center
This school is full of
those things--big ones.

00:09:05.462 --> 00:09:08.006 position:50% align:center
I can't be scared all the time.

00:09:09.883 --> 00:09:12.052 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] Seems like Yulia's
only able to see smaller,

00:09:12.135 --> 00:09:13.928 position:50% align:center
