It's not a crime last I checked.

00:09:19.601 --> 00:09:22.604 position:50% align:center
For sure! I'm just
sort of curious is all.

00:09:22.687 --> 00:09:23.980 position:50% align:center
[YULIA gasps]

00:09:24.064 --> 00:09:26.900 position:50% align:center
I don't have anyone to eat with;
what do you expect?

00:09:26.983 --> 00:09:28.526 position:50% align:center
