come sit with us?

00:09:28.610 --> 00:09:31.488 position:50% align:center
Beats the toilet, am I right?

00:09:31.571 --> 00:09:33.490 position:50% align:center
Here, this one's safe.

00:09:33.573 --> 00:09:35.909 position:50% align:center
[YULIA gasps]

00:09:40.497 --> 00:09:42.540 position:50% align:center
Now, we're havin' a good
ol' fashioned bread party!

00:09:42.624 --> 00:09:45.043 position:50% align:center
