00:09:45.126 --> 00:09:47.796 position:50% align:center
Whatever, whatever.

00:09:49.714 --> 00:09:51.049 position:50% align:center
[MIKO chuckles]

00:09:57.889 --> 00:10:00.266 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] I was hoping
I'd never see that guy again

00:10:00.350 --> 00:10:02.227 position:50% align:center
and now he's my teacher?

00:10:02.310 --> 00:10:04.562 position:50% align:center
I love the creamy
filling in these!

00:10:04.646 --> 00:10:06.147 position:50% align:center
[YULIA]
Mm-hm.

00:10:06.231 --> 00:10:09.067 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] My friends are better off
not knowing about these things.

00:10:09.150 --> 00:10:12.153 position:50% align:center
I'll have to keep them
safe any way I can.

00:10:16.449 --> 00:10:18.827 position:50% align:center
Better not look.

00:10:18.910 --> 00:10:20.328 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:10:29.963 --> 00:10:32.007 position:50% align:center
[HANA]
Mm! That's the stuff!

00:10:32.090 --> 00:10:34.759 position:50% align:center
Always best to
keep it simple, right?

00:10:39.431 --> 00:10:40.348 position:50% align:center
[YULIA, HANA gasp]

00:10:40.432 --> 00:10:42.100 position:50% align:center
You okay, Miko?

00:10:42.183 --> 00:10:44.019 position:50% align:center
A June bug flew in my eye.

00:10:44.102 --> 00:10:47.022 position:50% align:center
Ah, that really sucks!
That must've hurt!

00:10:47.105 --> 00:10:50.442 position:50% align:center
Those things are gargantuan!
Was it a boy bug or a girl bug?

00:10:50.525 --> 00:10:52.318 position:50% align:center
Ah, heh... What am I saying?

00:10:52.402 --> 00:10:54.112 position:50% align:center
That doesn't matt--

00:11:06.750 --> 00:11:10.712 position:50% align:center
[STAFF 09A] Come one, come all
to the House of Horrors!

00:11:10.795 --> 00:11:12.422 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER 09A]
Some Halloween thing.

00:11:12.505 --> 00:11:14.466 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER 09B]
They went all-out.

00:11:14.549 --> 00:11:16.718 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER 09C]
It's probably super lame.

00:11:19.012 --> 00:11:21.222 position:50% align:center
Hana, you don't have to do this.

00:11:21.306 --> 00:11:22.682 position:50% align:center
But donuts!

00:11:22.766 --> 00:11:24.351 position:50% align:center
That was so scary!

00:11:24.434 --> 00:11:25.560 position:50% align:center
Yeah, no kidding!

00:11:25.643 --> 00:11:27.437 position:50% align:center
[STAFF 09A]
Ooh! Congrats on your escape!

00:11:27.520 --> 00:11:29.147 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMERS gasp]

00:11:29.230 --> 00:11:30.815 position:50% align:center
