00:11:35.737 --> 00:11:38.406 position:50% align:center
So, you're more hungry
than you are scared.

00:11:38.490 --> 00:11:40.784 position:50% align:center
Haunted houses don't bother me.

00:11:40.867 --> 00:11:43.661 position:50% align:center
I'm so glad you're here!

00:11:43.745 --> 00:11:47.916 position:50% align:center
Aww! I know I can get
through this with your help!

00:11:47.999 --> 00:11:50.210 position:50% align:center
I'm totally dedicating
those donuts to you!

00:11:50.293 --> 00:11:52.003 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
A haunted house, huh?

00:11:52.087 --> 00:11:53.797 position:50% align:center
This could be good.

00:11:59.803 --> 00:12:01.471 position:50% align:center
