00:12:02.972 --> 00:12:05.850 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] Maybe it'll be
a good training exercise.

00:12:06.851 --> 00:12:09.396 position:50% align:center
[STAFF 09A]
Alrighty, next in line, please!

00:12:10.563 --> 00:12:12.482 position:50% align:center
[STAFF 09A]
Go get that stamp!

00:12:14.109 --> 00:12:16.277 position:50% align:center
[CUSTOMER 09E shrieks]

00:12:16.361 --> 00:12:19.823 position:50% align:center
[HANA yelps]
Protect me!

00:12:19.906 --> 00:12:20.782 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:12:20.865 --> 00:12:22.200 position:50% align:center
[YULIA groans]

00:12:22.283 --> 00:12:24.244 position:50% align:center
[HANA gasps]
Wait! Miko!

00:12:24.327 --> 00:12:26.705 position:50% align:center
[door squeaks]

00:12:26.788 --> 00:12:29.833 position:50% align:center
