my heart is ready yet.

00:12:41.052 --> 00:12:42.595 position:50% align:center
Whoa.

00:12:42.679 --> 00:12:45.515 position:50% align:center
This is creepy! This is crazy!

00:12:46.808 --> 00:12:49.436 position:50% align:center
[HANA whimpers]
It's so dark!

00:12:57.027 --> 00:12:59.320 position:50% align:center
[HANA whimpers]

00:12:59.404 --> 00:13:01.990 position:50% align:center
