00:13:12.083 --> 00:13:14.669 position:50% align:center
[HANA whimpers]

00:13:18.631 --> 00:13:24.637 position:50% align:center
[HANA whimpers]

00:13:24.721 --> 00:13:27.932 position:50% align:center
[YULIA chuckles]
What a joke.

00:13:28.016 --> 00:13:31.436 position:50% align:center
This maze is mere child's play
for those of us with the sight.

00:13:31.519 --> 00:13:35.273 position:50% align:center
With talents like mine, I'll
claim those free donuts easily!

00:13:37.525 --> 00:13:39.486 position:50% align:center
--[MIKO grunts]
--[HANA, YULIA] Mm?

00:13:41.738 --> 00:13:42.489 position:50% align:center
[BAGFACE 09A grunts]

00:13:42.572 --> 00:13:43.365 position:50% align:center
Huh?!

00:13:43.448 --> 00:13:44.741 position:50% align:center
Oh, no! Look out!

00:13:44.824 --> 00:13:46.201 position:50% align:center
--[MIKO gasps]
--[BAGFACE 09A grunts]

00:13:46.284 --> 00:13:49.412 position:50% align:center
[HANA screaming]

00:13:49.496 --> 00:13:51.414 position:50% align:center
